                {
                    "id": 1,
                    "img": "",
                    "faIcon": "",
                    "faIconColors": {"bg": "", "fill": ""},
                    "locales": {
                        "ru": {
                            "text": "<p>Я {{fullstack разработчик}} из [[Ташкента]]. Пишу веб-приложения на <b>React</b>, мобильные приложения на <b>React Native</b> и <b>Flutter/Dart</b>, бэкенд на <b>FastAPI + PostgreSQL</b>.</p><p>Разрабатываю <b>Telegram-боты</b> на Python с интеграцией AI (Anthropic API), автоматизирую процессы и деплою на Railway и Render.</p><p>Окончил MDIST Computer Information Systems for Business. Открыт для новых проектов!</p>"
                        },
                        "en": {
                            "text": "<p>I'm a {{fullstack developer}} from [[Tashkent]]. I build web apps with <b>React</b>, mobile apps with <b>React Native</b> and <b>Flutter/Dart</b>, and backends with <b>FastAPI + PostgreSQL</b>.</p><p>I also build <b>Telegram bots</b> in Python with AI integration (Anthropic API), automate workflows, and deploy to Railway and Render.</p><p>Graduated from MDIST Computer Information Systems for Business. Open to new projects!</p>"
                        },
                        "uz": {
                            "text": "<p>Men [[Toshkent]]dan {{fullstack dasturchi}}man. <b>React</b> bilan veb-ilovalar, <b>React Native</b> va <b>Flutter/Dart</b> bilan mobil ilovalar, <b>FastAPI + PostgreSQL</b> bilan backend yozaman.</p><p>Python'da <b>Telegram-botlar</b> yarataman: AI integratsiya (Anthropic API), avtomatlashtirish, Railway va Render'ga deploy.</p><p>MDIST Computer Information Systems for Business bitirganman. Yangi loyihalarga ochiqman!</p>"
                        }
                    }
                }
            ]
        },

